data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: To setup hardware: 1. Click "Solution File" box and location .sln folder to open. 2. Click "Config. Folder" box and locate configuration folder to apply. 3. Click "Add configuration to solution" and follow the on screen prompts. 4. Select "NO" if asked to restore any links.

data.name: textBox2.Text
data.value: To create configuration: 1. Select location for the config folder. 2. Setup folder 3. Open solution 4. Create mappings 5. Clear mappings 6. Export Axis XMLs 7. Export IO XMLs 8. ???Export Declarations for PLC??? 9. ???Export IO List???
